title: SingOut Cambridge
description:
Sing Out is back and we are looking forward to singing some new pieces this term, including ‘This is me’ from the Greatest Showman. Sing Out Cambridge is a friendly choir for the LGBT+ community. There is no audition and you don’t need to be able to read music.

Rehearsals run every Monday until Monday 17 December, with a break for half term.

Email cambslgbtchoir@gmail.com to find out more details such as venue and access.
